{"tid":1498165,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於物理學問題，（丫杈射爆眼罩？）","createTime":"2019-08-23T09:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T10:11:55.000Z","uid":213661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00cc6e68301043e0802a79fed5bdcd88b745c02a","tid":1498165,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"簡單物理，E=mv^2 /2。3m這型號眼罩能抵抗時速146的1/4吋鋼珠，假設質量為20g，需要16.5焦耳動能。<br />\n<br />\n假設0%能量損耗，鋼珠20g，要加速至40.56m/s，即是時速146公里，#她的丫杈要146磅。//<br />\n<br />\n想知其實段野有冇錯？<br />\n另外個假設係0%能量損耗，係咪即係未計個拉力？<br />\n如果加埋隻手去拉個到力，應該又點計？<br />\n<br />\n非物理人，想明白段野再去解釋比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d218013eb17b9c1bf22451924f17380e247ad9","tid":1498165,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:41:00.000Z","msg":"你唔記得計出口術影響，<br />\n話穿就穿到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad157ba4c78e9be6f604350afca8e1c9dbbe936f","tid":1498165,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:50:43.000Z","msg":"毅進物理學 唔係專家唔會解到 (好似醫生都解到 但全港得一個)<br />\n所以慳番D時間口水心機 做其他有意義嘅事"},{"pid":"b447fc88f8d3fbfeb7b91ab29bb07037b57bac35","tid":1498165,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"唔明最後嗰步點計出146磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e5ef6ae3e018951a85df10ee2b5f60293133cf","tid":1498165,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"我就咁計, 唔知啱唔啱<br />\nKE = 16.5J<br />\nWork done = Force * distance<br />\n假設Force成個過程不變, 丫叉彈射部份長20cm=0.2m<br />\n16.5 = F*0.2<br />\nF = 82.5N<br />\n除以g, 約等於8.41kg質量物件之重力, 即約18.5磅...?"},{"pid":"d6fca28f4bbf9353eeaad56dc47e817326be41f7","tid":1498165,"uid":251736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"咁簡單，用毅進制咪得囉"},{"pid":"415971e895de23a227282bc74ead171217851524","tid":1498165